---
export const prerender = true;

import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Rabbit Holes" description="Learn about Rabbit Holes, a curiosity-driven blog exploring technology, ideas, and discoveries. Find your next intellectual adventure to explore.">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="page-label">About</div>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Bhuvan</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Searching for new rabbit holes</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <p>Hi, I'm Bhuvan and I like tumbling down weird and wonderful rabbit holes. I like knowing random things and I think there's a certain joy in being a dilettante.</p>

      <p>It's not just me—everyone likes discovering new things, but for whatever reason, most people lose that ability to experience awe and wonder. It's tempting to blame social media apps and smartphones for this pathology, but that's too simplistic—they're not the only reason people seem to have become incurious and, perhaps more tragically, okay with being so.</p>

      <p>This blog is an attempt for me to continue slipping into weird rabbit holes and share them. The hope here is that whatever I share might trip fellow travelers on the internet and send them sliding down a rabbit hole.</p>

      <p>The goal isn't to be an expert on everything, but to maintain a sense of wonder about the world. Sometimes the most interesting insights come from wandering without a destination in mind.</p>

      <div class="quote-block">
        <blockquote>
          "Lastly, I confess that I have as vast contemplative ends, as I have moderate civil ends: for I have taken all knowledge to be my province."
          <cite><a href="https://paperlanterns.ink/letter/bacon-burghley-1592/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Francis Bacon</a></cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <h2>Philosophy</h2>
      <blockquote class="einstein-quote">
        "The important thing is not to stop questioning. Curiosity has its own reason for existence. One cannot help but be in awe when he contemplates the mysteries of eternity, of life, of the marvelous structure of reality. It is enough if one tries merely to comprehend a little of this mystery each day."
        <cite>Albert Einstein</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="mailto:bhuvan@bebhuvan.com" class="social-link">Email</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/bebhuvan" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
        <a href="https://bhuvan.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">Substack</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bebhuvan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>

      <h2>Colophon</h2>
      <p>This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>, enhanced with AI assistance from Claude, and hosted on Cloudflare Pages. The design is inspired by the clean, content-first ethos of early web blogging.</p>
      <p>Typography is set in Crimson Pro and Outfit for optimal reading. The color palette centers around a warm coral (#e87653) to create an inviting, accessible experience.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .about-container {
      max-width: var(--width-content);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .page-header {
      padding: 100px 0 80px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .page-label {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--color-text-light);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 68px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .about-content {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      padding-bottom: 120px;
    }

    .about-content p {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .about-content p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .about-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-top: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      letter-spacing: -0.018em;
      color: var(--color-text-primary);
    }

    .about-content h2:first-child {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    /* Francis Bacon quote - Editorial treatment */
    .quote-block {
      margin: 80px 0;
      padding: 48px 0 48px 56px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232, 118, 83, 0.02) 0%, transparent 100%);
      position: relative;
    }

    .quote-block blockquote {
      font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .quote-block blockquote cite {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .quote-block blockquote cite::before {
      content: '— ';
    }

    .quote-block blockquote cite a {
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .quote-block blockquote cite a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Einstein quote - Same as Bacon quote */
    .einstein-quote {
      margin: 80px 0;
      padding: 48px 0 48px 56px;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232, 118, 83, 0.02) 0%, transparent 100%);
      position: relative;
      font-family: 'Crimson Pro', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .einstein-quote cite {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .einstein-quote cite::before {
      content: '— ';
    }

    /* Social links */
    .social-links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .social-link {
      font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--color-accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
    }

    .social-link:hover {
      background: var(--color-accent);
      color: var(--color-bg);
      border-color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    /* Mobile responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-container {
        padding: 0 24px;
      }

      .page-header {
        padding: 60px 0 60px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 40px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .about-content {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 80px;
      }

      .about-content h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-top: 60px;
      }

      .quote-block {
        margin: 60px 0;
        padding: 36px 0 36px 40px;
      }

      .quote-block blockquote {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .einstein-quote {
        margin: 60px 0;
        padding: 36px 0 36px 40px;
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .social-links {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 12px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .about-container {
        padding: 0 var(--space-md);
      }

      .social-links {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
